\]

First factor under one radical and cancel common factors:

\[
\frac{\sqrt{56x^5y^4}}{\sqrt{2xy^3}}
=\sqrt{\frac{56x^5y^4}{2xy^3}}
=\sqrt{28x^4y}
=\sqrt{4\cdot7\;x^4\;y}
