\]

First combine under one cube root:  
\[
\frac{\sqrt[3]{48a^3b^6}}{\sqrt[3]{3a^{-1}b^3}}
= \sqrt[3]{\frac{48a^3b^6}{3a^{-1}b^3}}
= \sqrt[3]{16\,a^{3-(-1)}\,b^{6-3}}
= \sqrt[3]{16\,a^4\,b^3}.
\]
Now pull out the perfect cubes \(8a^3b^3\):  
\[
\sqrt[3]{16\,a^4\,b^3}
= \sqrt[3]{8\,a^3\,b^3\cdot 2a}
= \sqrt[3]{8}\,\sqrt[3]{a^3}\,\sqrt[3]{b^3}\,\sqrt[3]{2a}
=2ab\,\sqrt[3]{2a}.
\]
Answer: \(\displaystyle 2ab\sqrt[3]{2a}\).

