To rationalize the denominator, multiply top and bottom by the conjugate \((\sqrt r+\sqrt5)\):  

\[
\frac{\sqrt r+\sqrt5}{\sqrt r-\sqrt5}
\;\times\;
\frac{\sqrt r+\sqrt5}{\sqrt r+\sqrt5}
\;=\;
